            <h2>Overview</h2>

            <p>The Doorway Pullup Bar is a convenient and versatile piece of home workout equipment. It fits in most standard doorways and allows you to perform a variety of upper body exercises, including pullups, chinups, and hanging leg raises. Designed for ease of use and durability, it provides a solid option for those looking to improve their fitness from the comfort of their own home. With its compact design, this pullup bar is an ideal choice for those who want to enhance their workout routines without taking up too much space.</p>

            <p>Whether you're a beginner or an advanced athlete, the doorway pullup bar can support your fitness journey. It's simple to install and doesn't require permanent fixtures, making it a flexible option for renters or those with limited space. The Doorway Pullup Bar is perfect for individuals looking to strengthen their upper body and improve overall fitness levels.</p>

        </section>



        <!-- Key Features Section -->

        <section id="features">

            <h2>Key Features</h2>

            <p>The Doorway Pullup Bar comes with several key features that make it a popular choice among fitness enthusiasts. These include:</p>

            <ul>

                <li>Sturdy construction, supporting up to 300 lbs., allowing users of various body types to train safely.</li>

                <li>Non-slip grips for added comfort and stability, ensuring a secure hold during workouts.</li>

                <li>Fits most standard doorframes (24" to 32" wide), providing versatility for different home setups.</li>

                <li>Multiple grip positions for targeting different muscle groups, helping you maximize your workout efficiency.</li>

                <li>Easy installation with no permanent modifications required, making it user-friendly and convenient.</li>

            </ul>

        </section>



        <!-- Pros Section -->

