                <li>Durable and capable of supporting a wide range of body types, making it suitable for all users.</li>

                <li>Easy to install and remove without damaging doorframes, giving flexibility to renters.</li>

                <li>Affordable price point compared to other gym equipment, making fitness accessible to everyone.</li>

                <li>Versatile for a wide range of exercises beyond just pullups, including chin-ups and leg raises, enhancing workout variety.</li>

            </ul>

        </section>



